    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>Notesnook is a free (as in speech) and open source note taking app focused on user privacy and ease of use. To ensure zero knowledge principles, Notesnook encrypts everything on your device using `XChaCha20-Poly1305` and `Argon2`.

Notesnook is our **proof** that privacy does _not_ (always) have to come at the cost of convenience. Our goal is to provide users peace of mind and 100% confidence that their notes are safe and secure. The decision to go fully open source is one of the most crucial steps towards that.

**32 bit users**: This package is not available for 32 bit users.

**Please Note**: This is an automatically updated package. If you find it is out of date by more than a day or two, please contact the maintainer(s) and let them know the package is no longer updating correctly.</description>
    <summary>A fully open source and end-to-end encrypted note taking alternative to Evernote.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>## What's Changed
* Use newer appimage bundler by @thecodrr in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9744
* web: fix scrollbar blocking date in compact note list item by @01zulfi in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9719
* ui: fix submenu cutting off when there are a lot of lazy items by @01zulfi in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9739
* Fix crash on non-paddle related iframe events by @thecodrr in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9747
* desktop: Stop urgent reminder causes segfault &amp; app freeze on Linux. by @NeedsChloesure in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9737
* web: show titlebar on auth pages by @01zulfi in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9093
* core: Limit note subtitle length. by @NeedsChloesure in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9732
* Small refactor to make the web build pass by @thecodrr in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9761
* editor: fix crash in backspace handler by @01zulfi in https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/pull/9740

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/streetwriters/notesnook/compare/v3.3.15...v3.3.16</releaseNotes>
